\begin_inset Formula $y_{n}$
\end_inset

 uses almost all the data to infer 
\begin_inset Formula $\theta$
\end_inset

.
 Very little influenced by the prior when 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

 is not small.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
